{{> ui/page-header title="Document Store" icon="icon-[tabler--database]" class="mb-1"}}

<p class="mb-6 text-base-content/80">
    EmailEngine can sync emails to a document store for caching and local processing.
</p>

{{#> ui/stat-card variant="error" title="Deprecation Notice" icon="icon-[tabler--alert-circle]" class="mb-6"}}
<p class="mb-2">The Document Store feature in EmailEngine has been deprecated. This decision was made due
    to ongoing challenges in maintaining consistent synchronization between email accounts and their
    mirrored content on the ElasticSearch server.</p>
<ul class="list-disc ps-6">
    <li>The Document Store feature will not be removed from EmailEngine, and you can continue to use it
        as per your current needs.</li>
    <li>However, please be aware that as a deprecated feature, it will no longer receive new
        updates or enhancements.</li>
</ul>
{{/ui/stat-card}}

<nav class="tabs tabs-bordered mb-6" aria-label="Document store sections">
    <a class="tab{{#if documentStoreSettings}} tab-active{{/if}}" href="/admin/config/document-store">Settings</a>
    <a class="tab{{#if documentStorePreProcessing}} tab-active{{/if}}"
        href="/admin/config/document-store/pre-processing">Pre-processing</a>
    <a class="tab{{#if documentStoreChat}} tab-active{{/if}}" href="/admin/config/document-store/chat">Chat with
        emails {{> ui/badge label="beta" class="badge-sm ms-1"}}</a>
    <a class="tab{{#if documentStoreMappings}} tab-active{{/if}}"
        href="/admin/config/document-store/mappings">Field mappings</a>
</nav>
